cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.PL. 

The paper deals with solving hard problems more efficiently, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of treewidth as a parameter is a topic in logic and computation (cs.LO). The proposed graph representations and dynamic programming algorithms involve data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). Finally, the paper deals with answer set programming (ASP), which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
